Description: Fragment of rim of large, probably black-figured, North Ionian pottery plate; flaring sofa rim with ridge at junction with floor inside. Cream slip; outside reserved; interior: between bands, guilloche with spikes in interstices.
Curator's comments: Almost certainly from same plate as 1965,0930.465.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (GG.1046)
